<p>Van Gogh must be referring to the painting <hi xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" rend="italics">Ravine </hi>(<rs xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" type="artwork" ref="artwork.xml#ill_2881">F 661 / JH 1871</rs>); in an earlier letter he had told Theo that it was not yet dry (<ref xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" target="let836.xml">see letter 836</ref>).</p>
